A relation with the functional Schrodinger representation  

In this section we explore how the seemingly unusual precanonical 
quantization of YM theory is related to the familiar canonical 
quantization in the functional Schrodinger representation. 


Canonical quantization of pure YM theory. A reminder.  


Let us briefly recall the functional Schrodinger representation 
of the YM theory in the temporal gauge  
.  
